            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Gemini: Your Personalized AI Assistant</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                Gemini can help personalize learning, automate administrative tasks, and generate creative content, freeing up valuable time to focus on student engagement and growth. Explore "Gems" – customized Gemini chatbots (AI assistants) – that you can define with specific personas, instructions, tone, and audience to achieve predictable, time-saving results.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-gray-700">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-2">Ways to Use Gems:</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg space-y-1">
                        <li><strong>Lesson Plan Generator:</strong> Quickly draft outlines, objectives, and activities.</li>
                        <li><strong>Content Creator:</strong> Generate differentiated questions or reading passages.</li>
                        <li><strong>Feedback Assistant:</strong> Structure assessment criteria with a "Rubric Creator Gem."</li>
                        <li><strong>Idea Brainstormer:</strong> Discover new project ideas or unit themes.</li>
                        <li><strong>Communication Drafts:</strong> Draft emails or announcements for parents.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-2">What are Gems?</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg space-y-1">
                        <li>Customized Gemini chatbots (AI assistants).</li>
                        <li>Define their persona, instructions, tone, and audience.</li>
                        <li>Eliminate repetitive prompting for efficient, time-saving results.</li>
                        <li>Create new Gems or customize premade ones.</li>
                        <li>Ability to upload files to Gem instructions.</li>
                    </ul>
